Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.62,0:00:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.50,0:00:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为天气不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.96,0:00:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不懂啊 椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.50,0:00:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来这里可不是因为天气好 是因为没有人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对 你本来就不喜欢职员室
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.30,0:00:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的也挺丰盛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.49,0:00:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你天天都检查学生的便当吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定好了?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.27,0:00:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.10,0:00:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去说了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.40,0:01:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.97,0:01:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 因为是姐姐决定好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
